
INSTALL 
cd /home/mongo/MongoGEN

Replica Setup 
./install-replica.run


S3METETA UTILITIES
mdisksize         - MongoDB Datbase size check
mconnection       - Number of connection checking
mopplog           - MongoDB Replica Opplog Status
mstart            - MongoDB Instance Start
mstop             - MongoDB Instance Stop
mstart            - MongoDB Instance Restart
mrepstatus        - MongoDB Replica Status
mpriority         - MongoDB Replica Priority Status
MUNINSTALL        - MongoDB Instance uninstall
mcreateuser       - MongoDB User Create
mdump             - MongoDB Instance Backup
mrestore          - MongoDB Instance Restore
mdumpDB           - MongoDB Database Backup
mDBrestore        - MongoDB Database Restore
mcoldump          - MongoDB Collection Backup
mcolrestore       - MongoDB Collection Backup
mpitrbackup       - MongoDB Point Time Backup
mpitrrestore      - MongoDB Point Time Recovery
